# Unit Testing Conventions

## Pre-Development Checklist

Before writing tests, read:

- [ ] `conventions.md` - Test naming, structure, and organization
- [ ] `mock-strategies.md` - When and how to use mocks
- [ ] `fixtures.md` - Test data and fixture patterns
- [ ] `coverage.md` - Coverage requirements and strategies

---

## Overview

This directory contains testing conventions and best practices.

## Contents

- **conventions.md** - Test file naming, test structure, assertion patterns
- **mock-strategies.md** - Mocking strategies, when to use real vs mock dependencies
- **fixtures.md** - Test data management, fixture factories, cleanup
- **coverage.md** - Coverage targets, what to test, what to skip

